<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>LegitBank - Wyłącz 2FA</title>
    <link
        href="data:image/x-icon;base64,"
        rel="icon" type="image/x-icon">
    <style>
        h1 {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, orange, yellow, green, cyan, blue, violet);
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            font-size: 50px;
        }

        body {
            font-family: "Comic Sans MS", "Comic Sans";
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #22d71d, #fd2ef6, #9b5300);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px black;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .form-group input,
        .form-group textarea {
            font-family: "Comic Sans MS", "Comic Sans";
            font-weight: bold;
            width: 98%;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .form-group textarea {
            resize: none;
        }

        .submit {
            font-family: "Comic Sans MS", "Comic Sans";
            font-weight: bold;
            background-color: #00af3a;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .submit:hover {
            background-color: green;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>LegitBank<sup>TM</sup></h1>
        <h2>Czy na pewno chcesz wyłączyć 2FA?</h2>
        <h3> <a href="/confirm-2fa-off">TAK</a> <a href="/account">NIE</a></h3>
    </div>
</body>

</html>